{"tid":440502,"cid":14,"subCid":0,"title":"究竟點先搵到自己鍾意ge 工？","createTime":"2017-10-19T00:00:04.000Z","updateTime":"2017-10-19T01:31:37.000Z","uid":153784,"like":2,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"55d50c483d020a164fc0638d0dcbd7310eb5e3d8","tid":440502,"uid":153784,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-19T00:00:04.000Z","msg":"上年讀完master 今年開始做野<br />\n返黎搵左好耐都搵唔到工 後尾搵到一份算高人工ge sales<br />\n本身覺得自己幾岩做 份工時間彈性 <br />\n腦細肯教野又好hands off <br />\n開頭仲要好快就開到幾張單<br />\n但 後尾做做下 覺得自己根本講野唔叻 <br />\n成日講野1999 最近又搵唔到客仔 <br />\n或者搵到最尾因為自己sell同解釋得唔夠好而冇左<br />\n除左自己能力之外 份工工時好長 平均做10-11個鐘 <br />\n放完工真係冇心情做其他野<br />\n同埋唔知係壓力定其他原因 <br />\n我真係病左3、4次返左呢份工之後<br />\n<br />\n做左半年 呢排做到dup dup 地 成日想搵工<br />\n上jobsdb LinkedIn <br />\n一係就我做唔到 唔係就冇興趣或者我冇經驗<br />\n同埋冇理由係度半年就走 cv會好7...<br />\n<br />\n我又係度諗 其實係咪因為做d 野out of my comfort zone. 所以自己咁唔想做 其實係自己懶去學<br />\n<br />\n呢排真係連返工都冇心機做野<br />\n覺得自己好廢<br />\n又大壓力<br />\n唉<br />\n點先搵到自己有興趣又能力做到ge工？ <br />\n我應該quit？"},{"pid":"2aed10ec96f1a7c3602909774c05f7c6ab6d3b58","tid":440502,"uid":86390,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-19T00:01:10.000Z","msg":"巴打係咪做傳銷<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"78077d19734435f271f0fbf3524d809ce73beb3a","tid":440502,"uid":58140,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-19T00:03:04.000Z","msg":"香港地。。。唉"},{"pid":"9bd90dfa8902e19865caf22868f3d61d624fd586","tid":440502,"uid":8561,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-19T00:03:14.000Z","msg":"唔適合咪再轉，轉到鐘意為止<br />\n<br />\n我都有幾份工，做左個零月無做，唔放Cv 都無問題。"},{"pid":"fce3aeb48009401ee6a7a10dcee88d25d52f2bc2","tid":440502,"uid":101390,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-19T00:32:43.000Z","msg":"咁要睇你下份工想做咩多<br />\n如果唔等錢洗 唔適合梗係快d 走<br />\n利申： 等錢洗 10.5 k 工做半年即走"},{"pid":"927aa76a8b4728431c38cbbbbf05d6bdc7a0e50f","tid":440502,"uid":8748,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-19T00:41:40.000Z","msg":"巴打你讀咩科先 冇自己專業技能咩"},{"pid":"4a2dfcbaf8234b80be5cbc1d3fba3b895c6a8ce7","tid":440502,"uid":153784,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-19T01:05:14.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>巴打係咪做傳銷<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n唔係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"78060f30068cb5984a482be7552839a227e94714","tid":440502,"uid":153784,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-19T01:06:03.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>巴打你讀咩科先 冇自己專業技能咩</blockquote><br />\n19bba <br />\n都唔知做乜好"},{"pid":"3f64798e0c047aa7a927a3a9ab87bc2cd6c69437","tid":440502,"uid":153784,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-19T01:08:09.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>咁要睇你下份工想做咩多<br />\n如果唔等錢洗 唔適合梗係快d 走<br />\n利申： 等錢洗 10.5 k 工做半年即走</blockquote><br />\n我等錢洗嫁 屋企人供左我讀master<br />\n都用左好多錢 我份工老底唔低<br />\n唔知仲有咩工好簡<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3e2588f57501d294e140ed1d0757f025c75c4174","tid":440502,"uid":2357,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-19T01:09:09.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>巴打你讀咩科先 冇自己專業技能咩</blockquote><br />\n19bba <br />\n都唔知做乜好</blockquote><br />\n半年走左，人工加左"},{"pid":"2a7b179cf34e2f73eba93ef66c796b2678309d44","tid":440502,"uid":28052,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-19T01:10:20.000Z","msg":"自己鍾意嘅工就向興趣方面發展<br />\n但係自己鍾意同份工好無做好無返又係另外一回事"},{"pid":"1f3069993427f0dd771d87775686ac85c1f5d843","tid":440502,"uid":1285,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-19T01:31:37.000Z","msg":"我覺得唔好一睇完就覺得做唔到先<br />\n我本身都唔叻講野，都膽粗粗走去試下去做sales<br />\n學下身邊同事點sell客同解釋俾人聽，依加都返得好開心下<img src=\"/assets/f